         <abstract id="aspace_336ce294a48d2a73f2b6a408882b2524">The records consist of development files, committee records, financial reports, budgets, and notes of the deputy university librarian, Yale University. The records document library departments and collections, personnel, equipment requests, and the library's participation in the Research Libraries Group (RLG).</abstract>
